@startuml
title SQLTracer System Context

actor "Developer / Operator" as User
node "Application" as App
node "sqltracer.py\n(PostgreSQL Proxy + TUI/Headless)" as Tracer
database "PostgreSQL" as Pg
cloud "HashiCorp Vault\n(optional config source)" as Vault
file "Plain / Encrypted Config" as Config

User --> Tracer : run, monitor, inspect
App --> Tracer : PostgreSQL wire protocol traffic
Tracer --> Pg : forward traffic
Tracer --> Vault : read config via userpass
Tracer --> Config : load config files
Tracer --> User : TUI, headless stdout, export/report files

@enduml
